# OrchestraIQ FSM Editor — Environment Variables
# Copy this to .env.local and fill in your values

# Supabase Project (create at https://supabase.com/dashboard)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# Claude API (for FSM chat assistant — optional)
# Note: The Claude API key is injected automatically in claude.ai artifacts.
# For standalone deployment, you'd need to proxy through a backend to avoid
# exposing the key in the browser. For tomorrow's demo between two users,
# the chat feature works via the artifact sandbox or can be disabled.
